# Home Sensor Mosquitto ACL.
#
# Install path on Raspberry Pi:
#   /etc/mosquitto/acl.d/home-sensor.acl
#
# With acl_file configured, clients only have access to listed topics.

user home_sensor_gateway
topic write home/sensors/+
topic write home/air/+

user home_sensor_bridge
topic read home/sensors/+
topic read home/air/+
